<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Hlan lioah David khua chungah, Caw inn pakhat a rak um, Cu ka caw
 rawleinak kuang ah Mary nih a fa a thlim, Bawi Jesuh nun nem bik te,
 Cawkuang chungah a hngilh ko.

[V2]
 Van in vawlei ah a rung tum, Pathian zeizong te Bawipa, Bethlehem
 cawinn ah a chuak Cawkuang chungah khan an thlim, Rethei sifak mi sinah,
 Thiang tein leiah a nung.

[V3]
 Ngakchia a rak si lio vialte, A nu a rak pomtu kha, A dawt i a hmaizah
 ngaingai tha tein a zohkhenh fawn, Kannih ngakchia vialte hi, Amah bang
 si awk kan si.

[V4]
 A donghnak bik ah kan hmuh lai, Amah nih a kan dawt ca'h, Kha
 lungnemmi ngakchia te kha, Van ah khin kan Bawi a si, A umnak vanram nuam
 ah, A fale a kan hruai lai.

[V5]
 Caw inn chungah si ti loin, Sunparnak vancung khua ah, Pathian orhlei
 kam ah thu in, Kan hmuh lai, lianhngannak he, A fale cu arfi bang, Kan
 ceu lai, a kiang vel ah.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>DAVID KHUA CHUNGAH CH92</title>
<hymn_number>92</hymn_number>
</song>